WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.210 --> 00:00:02.800
Skillflow brings reusable review instructions

2
00:00:02.820 --> 00:00:05.115
into TYPO3. A team imports

3
00:00:05.135 --> 00:00:06.870
a skill, finds it by

4
00:00:06.890 --> 00:00:08.990
category or allowed tools, and

5
00:00:09.010 --> 00:00:10.945
assigns it to a workspace

6
00:00:10.965 --> 00:00:12.960
stage. When content reaches that

7
00:00:12.980 --> 00:00:14.920
stage, the selected reviews run

8
00:00:14.940 --> 00:00:17.075
and save suggestions for the

9
00:00:17.095 --> 00:00:19.540
editor. Nothing changes automatically;

10
00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:22.035
a person chooses what to

11
00:00:22.055 --> 00:00:24.830
accept. This adds consistent quality

12
00:00:24.850 --> 00:00:26.630
checks to the normal workflow.

13
00:00:26.650 --> 00:00:28.820
The feature page explains imports,

14
00:00:28.840 --> 00:00:30.720
triggers, and reports.
